Don't pay any attention whatsoever to idiots who flame you. You don't need
their approval--you need to mine diamonds of information from the mountains
of dirt.

There is an old adage "better to remain silent and be thought a fool than
to speak and remove all doubt". Another adage is "nothing ventured, nothing
gained".

Good luck!

